title: Solved Mysteries; or, Revelations of a City Detective
author: Macgovan, James.
snippet: In our next tour we took some places in Rose Street without much success. At length we landed in Elder Street, and one woman there, when asked if she knew of a Mary Shand, said, with great animation—

title: Mystifications /
author: Graham, Clementina Stirling
snippet: " In Elder Street ! that seems to me rather an expensive part of the town for a person in your circumstances."
